      "review_summary": "The branch adds a structured non-image fallback to `extractToolResultText`, plus helper tests for text-first behavior, data-URI redaction, circular serialization, and truncation.\n\nPR surface: Source +49, Tests +64. Total +113 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main returns no text for structured-only non-image content blocks, and the visible-output caller emits only when this helper returns text. I did not reproduce the live placeholder in a clean rebuilt OpenClaw session.",
